  "subject": "Force dgbuilder and odlsli-alpine docker push",
  "commit_message": "Force dgbuilder and odlsli-alpine docker push\n\n - hardcoded override for docker.skip.push for docker images that\n   are needed for CSIT\n - the solution provided here is not particularly elegant (I would\n   prefer to define these separately in maven build parameters\n   for these images for now, but couldn't immediately find an easy\n   way of doing that) so if you have a better idea of making this\n   happen, feel free to suggest/implement\n\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-3057\n\nSigned-off-by: Lasse Kaihlavirta <l.kaihlavirt@partner.samsung.com>\nChange-Id: I9427c5f301ffa43cc6c2ae8ab357f9e37890e1a1\n",
